name: r-rpmg
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '2.2-3' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rpmg
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RPMG_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RPMG/RPMG_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 74d5bada6a51d280296cb36fae4938c16ba9ed2fa37f3bfb60cf7c541c5b22b6

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RPMG')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RPMG')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=RPMG
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Really Poor Man's Graphical User Interface, used to create interactive R analysis
    sessions with simple R commands.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
